itemLabel: Princess Amelia of the United Kingdom
itemDescription: daughter of King George III of the United Kingdom

wikipedia_page.main: Princess Amelia of the United Kingdom (7 August 1783 – 2 November 1810) was the fifteenth and last child and sixth daughter of King George III of the United Kingdom and his wife, Charlotte of Mecklenburg-Strelitz. She was their first daughter to die and third child to die before them.
